{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/people/anneliese-dodds","content_id":"0411ea9e-11ae-47a2-a1bd-553614dccb4a","description":"Anneliese Dodds was Minister for Development at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office and Minister for Women and Equalities at the Department for Education from 8 July 2024 until 28 February 2025. She was elected as the MP for Oxford East in June 2017. Follow Anneliese on X/Twitter: @AnnelieseDodds","details":{"body":"<p>Anneliese Dodds was Minister for Development at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office and Minister for Women and Equalities at the Department for Education from 8 July 2024 until 28 February 2025. She was elected as the MP for Oxford East in June 2017.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n  <p>Follow Anneliese on X/Twitter:  <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://x.com/AnnelieseDodds\">@AnnelieseDodds</a></p>\n</div>\n","full_name":"Anneliese Dodds MP","image":{"alt_text":"The Rt Hon Anneliese Dodds MP","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66912df1fc8e12ac3edafbd5/s465_a-dodds.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":true},"document_type":"person","first_published_at":"2024-07-08T10:51:23+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/anneliese-dodds","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/anneliese-dodds","base_path":"/government/people/anneliese-dodds","content_id":"0411ea9e-11ae-47a2-a1bd-553614dccb4a","document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-02-28T16:33:20Z","schema_name":"person","title":"The Rt Hon Anneliese Dodds MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/anneliese-dodds","withdrawn":false}],"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"3a1eab3c-0035-4534-b5be-bb0ecf82a29c","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2025-02-28T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2024-07-08T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_a